		<description>Enhanced GUI to create, edit, assign and document Dataverse security roles.</description>
		<releaseNotes>
			This tool provides an advanced GUI to create, edid, assign and generate documentation for Dataverse security roles.
			v$version$: First version.
			
			Main features:
			- Create new roles or edit existing security roles with an advanced UI
			- Create and use privilege templates (a set of predefined privileges to be assigned to tables)
			- Predefined privilege templates
			- Clone roles
			- Check if a given role is actually used
			- Assign role to a user/team
			- Contextual help

			* For older releases go here: https://github.com/neronotte/Greg.Xrm/releases
